SBI SmartLife Agent is an Agentic AI-powered customer lifecycle platform designed to improve customer acquisition, digital adoption, and digital engagement in digital banking.

The platform creates a Customer Digital Twin for every user by analyzing onboarding status, transaction behavior, digital banking usage, preferences, and financial goals. A network of specialized AI agents continuously monitors customer activity and proactively guides users through their banking journey.

Unlike traditional banking chatbots that only respond to queries, SBI SmartLife Agent autonomously identifies customer needs and recommends the next best actions such as completing onboarding, activating UPI, enabling mobile banking, setting savings goals, or exploring relevant banking products.

The solution introduces a Digital Adoption Score that measures customer engagement with digital banking services and enables personalized interventions. Through continuous learning and real-time analytics, SBI SmartLife Agent helps banks reduce onboarding drop-offs, increase digital transactions, improve customer retention, and deliver highly personalized banking experiences at scale.
